title: X.Wordpress.Theme.v2.3.0-AKA-X.The.Theme
description:
Name: X The Theme
Type: Wordpress Theme
Release Date: 2 August 14
Version: 2.3.0
Columns: 4+
Compatible Browsers: IE9, IE10, IE11, Firefox, Safari, Opera, Chrome
Software Version: WordPress 3.9, 3.8, 3.7, 3.6
Compatible With: BuddyPress 2.0.x, WooCommerce 2.1.x, Gravity Forms
Documentation: Well Documented
High Resolution	Yes
Layout: Responsive
Files Included: Layered PSD, PHP Files, CSS Files, JS Files, PSD
Widget Ready: Yes

X was built upon the input of industry-leading experts. We consulted numerous individuals and asked them what sort of features they wanted to see in a theme from an SEO standpoint, design, feature-set, et cetera, and built their suggestions right into the theme. Forget the marketing speak, X truly delivers on what it promises.

This is complete, meaning, except for the Theme it contains: all PSD files, Documentations and Importable Democontent. 

If you like it, please support the creators and buy it! This theme seriously Kick Ass!
